11:19.980 --> 11:24.366
Montagnards were working.

11:28.514 --> 11:34.442
To my knowledge,

11:28.514 --> 11:34.442
they were not resettled. I think they remain in the 
mountains. Special forces working there. They

11:41.412 --> 11:47.059
were not located in the area. So I just don't have 
any knowledge or information. In the field, I

11:51.225 --> 11:53.408
understand that many the commanding officers 
were thought of as kings, and that whatever they

11:53.692 --> 11:59.721
