poor. They weren't well fed, and there were ways to

12:43.726 --> 12:49.913
take care of the troops whenever they were in the 
field. You required them to go out there and cut

12:49.933 --> 12:51.254
their hair. You required them to shave every day. 
we operated

12:53.682 --> 13:17.462
in the field continuously very seldom did we ever 
go back to a camp area where we could change clothes

12:53.682 --> 13:17.462
and take a shower when we did that was the first 
thing we did but also had fresh clothes blown into

12:53.682 --> 13:17.462
us where we just take off our old clothes put them 
back on and put them on a helicopter from shipping

13:17.982 --> 13:24.872
out to Washington and fresh them. I had a different 
type of rations in there other than the old C

13:24.892 --> 13:29.860
rations that we made. They were called the B 
rations. You got the dehydrated foods, hamburger

13:31.622 --> 13:44.301
patties, rice, ketchup, mustard, beans, things 
like that to supplement the C rations.

13:44.321 --> 13:45.002
The C rations is a high-nutrition, well-balanced 
ration. But it gets old. There are 12 types of

13:52.908 --> 13:57.873
meals, and that's all you get. And I was determined 
when I got there to eat those meals to keep my health

13:57.893 --> 14:03.840
up. And I found after three months in the field that 
I was even being selective in what I ate. And when

14:10.187 --> 14:16.153
you become selective, then you don't get that 
balanced diet that you ate in the spring. When that

14:16.808 --> 14:19.031
happens, people get sores. They get injured. 
Those injuries become sores, and you might have to

14:20.994 --> 14:28.084
evacuate someone to be treated because you get big 
sores.

14:30.908 --> 14:36.396
With the change of diet, we've corrected all of 
that. Another example, during the monsoons when

14:36.416 --> 14:46.090
it's so wet, you can get immersion, but you stay wet 
all the time. I had people... Our eyes should be on

14:47.116 --> 14:53.543
three pairs of socks, and we changed three times a 
day. Me on the move, your feet would get wet every

14:53.563 --> 14:57.948
time we would stop and take your socks off. But on a 
fresh pair, you'd rain those socks out and tuck

14:57.968 --> 15:05.696
them down on the inside of your trousers where your 
