harassment. Again, we were operating in a

21:28.780 --> 21:35.971
no-man's country where everyone was hostile. 
There were no females there, as I said, indicated

21:36.011 --> 21:39.477
they were back in the resettlement camps. Those 
camps were not guarded by U.S. forces, so there

21:40.047 --> 21:49.696
